<span data-as="p">Before opening a GHSA, verify all of these:</span>
<ol>
<li>Repro still works on latest <code>main</code> or latest release.</li>
<li>Report includes exact code path (<code>file</code>, function, line range) and tested version/commit.</li>
<li>Impact crosses a documented trust boundary (not just prompt injection).</li>
<li>Claim is not listed in <a href="https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/main/SECURITY.md#out-of-scope" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="link">Out of Scope</a>.</li>
<li>Existing advisories were checked for duplicates (reuse canonical GHSA when applicable).</li>
<li>Deployment assumptions are explicit (loopback/local vs exposed, trusted vs untrusted operators).</li>
</ol>
